title: S12 Ep101: Inside UFO's: True Accounts of Contact

description:
Today with the help of our guest, Preston Dennett we explore these questions;
Why are the aliens here? What is their agenda on our planet? Are they hostile or benevolent?
By digging into eye witness accounts of UFO & Alien sightings we seek answers from the people who have experienced them. PLUS a Brand New THEATER of the MIND with SyFy Channel's Fact or Fake Bill Murphy's Alien Encounter.
